{"tid":1572171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際輿論其實好簡單 無出現行刑式無差別攻擊就唔需要擔心","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:46:01.000Z","uid":258592,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fec520aff8b2cf49d828b657520e338bbc6e261","tid":1572171,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"燒野？燒死咗邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆玻璃？邊間銀行金鋪有被搶掠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非出現類似isis果種拍片斬首<br />\n或者燒死bb仔小朋友<br />\n即使黑警被人燒 係國際眼中都係自然生態現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一句到尾 西方政府幫唔幫你 只係國際秩序、意識形態同各種利益等等問題 （新冷戰局勢、經濟政治利益）<br />\n<br />\n而西方社會支唔支持你 係考驗我地公關做得夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下外國頭條大家就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估好似香港班偽中立撚咩 比人打就舉手搵老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa821f061852d69a63c4d57fba63bc42d4311b2","tid":1572171,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"［極重要］全民錫春袋！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1efae9ddce5f8b0fac09b99fb20d1956f9fa166","tid":1572171,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef08d67cdee8ac4c9e85ae9aedb0a5336cb12f2e","tid":1572171,"uid":33063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}